								"html": "<p>\n\tWhen you purchase a <strong>Salvation Army Honor Card</strong>, you’re not only celebrating someone special—you’re helping provide <strong>food, shelter, and care</strong> for neighbors in need right here in Greater Winston-Salem.\n</p>",
